nodes.text: Return of the Jedi Weekly 11 is the eleventh issue of Return of the Jedi Weekly, the continuation of the Marvel Star Wars UK series.
This issue reprints part two of the story printed in the US as Star Wars 75, along with part one of Star Wars 2.
The letters page contains a letter written by future Star Wars Insider contributor Mark Newbold under his fan-fic psyeudonym of Jan Lomona.
